===Etymology===
{{L.}} [[invocare]], to call upon

===Verb===
{{en-verb|invok|ing}}

# {{transitive}} To [[call]] upon someone for [[help]], [[assistance]] or [[guidance]], especially upon a [[god]].
# {{transitive}} To [[conjure]] up with [[incantation]]s.
# {{transitive}} {{computing}} To cause a [[program]] or [[subroutine]] to execute.

====Synonyms====
* ({{computing}} ''To cause a program or subroutine to execute'') [[call]], [[execute]], [[run]]

